HEADWORD: Rosland
<hw>Ros"land</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[W. <ets>rhos</ets> a
meadow, a moor + E. <ets>land</ets>.]</ety> <def>heathy land; land full
